edu.buffalo.cse562.checkpoint1.plan

Class SelectionNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.buffalo.cse562.checkpoint1.plan.PlanNode
      • edu.buffalo.cse562.checkpoint1.plan.PlanNode.Unary
        • edu.buffalo.cse562.checkpoint1.plan.SelectionNode

  • public class SelectionNode
extends PlanNode.Unary
    A concrete implementation of a relational plan operator representing a selection operator. A selection node has only a single feature: an Expression that evaluates to a boolean value when evaluated (e.g., Ship.Name = 'Enterprise').
